<item>
            <title>[CXF-4171] Static resource resolution not possible with CXFNonSpringJaxrsServlet</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-4171</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The title says it all. I wanted this to get a full WADL document, and found it&apos;s not supported.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I was able to do it only by changing the source code - adding bean.setStaticSubresourceResolution(true); to ResourceUtils:621 (before bean.setResourceClasses(resourceClasses) ) does the trick.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Since this requires source code modification or copy-pasting and overriding methods in both CXFNonSpringJaxrsServlet and ResourceUtils I think that there should be a config option similiar to jaxrs.application.address.ignore available for this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
